summary: SPIKE.esm incase your load order or patcher needs it and you dont know where to find it
descriptionHtml: ok first of all I didn't made this file I just found it and decided to upload it because I've been having a ton of problems with patchers asking for SPIKE.esm when it is no longer needs, so I found a mod which still and it in to use it in my load order and decided to share it so anyone else with this problem can find it in a easier way
author: someone else but me
